title: Truth Week: The Truth About a Hook Up
description:
Each morning this week the Dave Ryan Show is challenging ourselves to answer a tough question and tell the TRUTH.  
Day #1:  Have you ever hooked up with someone you were too good for and someone that was too good for you?
